## ðŸ’¡ Best Practices

### Template Design
- Use Handlebars syntax for dynamic content
- Leverage `askUser` for interactive prompts
- Use `askAgent` sparingly - it's expensive
- Prefer flat JSON schemas for structured data

### Agent Design
- Keep agents focused on a single responsibility
- Use clear color assignments for easy identification
- Document when to use each agent
- Make agents read-only when appropriate

### Skill Design
- Include clear examples in skill documentation
- Provide templates for common patterns
- Document prerequisites and dependencies
- Test skills in isolation before packaging

