### Skills Not Available
```bash
# Re-apply the package
tz apply --force

# Check symlinks
ls -la .claude/skills
```

### Templates Not Rendering
```bash
# Clear cache and regenerate
rm agents-cache.toml
tz apply --no-cache --force
```

### Package Validation Errors
```bash
# Validate package structure
tz validate

